<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4665710>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. — Capparis irenae Fici, sp.nov.: A, flowering branch; B, leaf base with stipular thorn; C, flower;D, dissected flower showing sepals and petals; E, stamens; F, gynophore and ovary. All from the holotype, Burley et al. 1946 (L). Drawn by S. Fici. Scale bars: A, 2 cm; B, 2 mm; C, D, F, 4 mm; E, 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4665710/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4665712>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Known distribution of Capparis irenae Fici, sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4665712/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

